cu_modifications.explanation: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU to an unreachable IP (10.0.0.1) will prevent NG-U interface binding and cause GTP-U tunnel establishment failure.
cu_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU 設定為不可達的 IP (10.0.0.1) 會阻止 NG-U 接口綁定，並導致 GTP-U 隧道建立失敗。

du_modifications.explanation: Setting remote_n_address to an unreachable IP (10.0.0.1) will prevent F1 remote network connection and cause CU-DU communication failure.
du_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 remote_n_address 設定為不可達的 IP (10.0.0.1) 會阻止 F1 遠端網路連接，並導致 CU-DU 通信失敗。
